{"lastModified":1771257321766,"uri":"c::8346777690::vessel::3a0626d0-4131-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nThe Oceanis 46 Stavros tou Notou is a sailing yacht produced by the French boat builder Beneteau. The yacht is named after a famous Greek song called “Stavros tou Notou”, which means “Southern Cross” in Greek.\n\nThe Oceanis 46 is a modern cruising yacht designed for comfortable and safe sailing. It has a spacious and well-ventilated cockpit, a large saloon with ample seating and four cabins. The yacht is designed to be easy to handle, even with a small crew, and features a modern sail plan and efficient hull design for fast and comfortable sailing.\n\nSome of the notable features of the Oceanis 46 Stavros tou Notou include:\n\nA spacious cockpit with twin steering wheels, large cockpit table, and plenty of storage\nA modern, airy interior with plenty of natural light and ventilation\nFour comfortable cabins\nTwo heads\nA well-equipped galley with ample storage and counter space\nA powerful yet easy-to-use sail plan, with a roller-furling mainsail and genoa\nA sturdy and reliable construction, built to high standards of safety and quality.\n\nOverall, the Oceanis 46 Stavros tou Notou is a well-designed and well-built sailing yacht that is ideal for cruising and comfortable living aboard.","blueprint":{"name":"STAVROS TOU NOTOU","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::3a0626d0-4131-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219::assets::eed126e0-4132-11f0-8e6a-4d2cd9a0bc5d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::3a0626d0-4131-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219::assets::eed4a950-4132-11f0-8e6a-4d2cd9a0bc5d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::3a0626d0-4131-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219::assets::eec9faf0-4132-11f0-8e6a-4d2cd9a0bc5d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::3a0626d0-4131-11f0-8ff3-a570d7d15219::assets::eec84d40-4132-11f0-8e6a-4d2cd9a0bc5d/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::3a0626d0-4131-11f0